->kops cluster create command:

kops create cluster --name mycluster.k8s.local --zones=eu-north-1a,eu-north-1b --master-count=1 --master-size=m7i-flex.large --master-volume-size=30 --node-count=3 --node-size=c7i-flex.large --node-volume-size=30 --image=ami-0a716d3f3b16d290c

->secrets create command for docker hub credentials---to be executed manually in kops cluster 

kubectl create secret docker-registry mysecret --docker-username=thrineshjogu --docker-password=Dasara@25 --docker-server=https://index.docker.io/v1/

->trivy --- take the command from offical document for latest version

curl -sfL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/aquasecurity/trivy/main/contrib/install.sh | sudo sh -s -- -b /usr/local/bin v0.67.2

->Sonarqube

docker run -d --name sonar -p 9000:9000 sonarqube:lts-community

